        // The other class can be formed by taking $a_n$ as the median, and $j$ elements smaller than it, and $j$ elements larger than it.
        //
        // A concrete construction:
        // Class 1: $\{a_0, a_1, \dots, a_{n-1}\}$
        // Class 2: $\{a_n, a_{n+1}, \dots, a_{2n-1}\}$
        // This is not valid.
