        // Class 2: $\{a_n, a_{n+1}, \dots, a_{2n-1}\}$
        //
        // This is the correct interpretation. The problem is asking for the difference between the $n$-th element and the $(n+1)$-th element (1-indexed) in the sorted array.
        // In 0-indexed, this is $a[n]$ and $a[n-1]$.
